pised suzy and vice versa at one point he refused to hire her anymore because suzy complained about the peanut paycheck she received from revlon richard avedon however after photographing other models for a particular revlon ad would call in suzy last minute sometimes late at night to do retakes with him this happened with stormy pink an ad suzy shot very late at night with a wild white horse in the ocean avedon would then tell revson that it was not suzy in the ad but a model named bubbles or another madeup name in  revlon became the first american cosmetics company to feature an african american model naomi sims in their advertising revlon was also noted for featuring models of a wide age range in the s including then yearold milla jovovich and then yearold audrey hepburn despite the successful campaigns of the s and s featuring models in particular cindy crawford revlon decided to drop fashion models and focus on movie stars among them kate bosworth jaime king halle berry susan sarandon melanie griffith julianne moore eva mendes jessica alba jennifer connelly beau garrett jessica biel olivia wilde emma stone and bond girls in  australian supermodel elle macpherson became a new spokesmodel for the company american actress jessica biel is the newest woman to model for the brand first shown in advertisements in january  main article list of revlon spokesmodels in  celebrity makeup artist gucci westman was hired as revlons global artistic director representing the company at runway shows and brand events and designing collections philanthropyedit becky gulsvig at revlon runwalk for cancer revlon is a corporate sponsor of several charity projects the largest of these is the revlon run walk a run and walk event held in new york and los angeles to raise money and awareness for breast and ovarian cancer revlon also supports other cancer charities such as look good feel better and the national breast cancer coalition and operates a mobile mammography clinic in and around oxford north carolina where the companys primary manufacturing operations are located in  revlon supported the development of a breast center at the university of california los angeles renamed revlonucla breast center the center is a wellknown institute for treatment and research of breast cancer and other breast diseases and disorders a revlon lip gloss shade whose proceeds support revlons cancer charities was also created in  in september  revlon with global artistic director gucci westman and spokesmodel halle berry hosted an event at fashions night out in new york city to raise funds for the jenesse center a los angeles organization for domestic violence victims revlon also hosted luncheons and various other events to benefit the center and partnered with online retailer drugstorecom to donate portions of lipstick sales to the organization see alsoedit list of revlon spokesmodels referencesedit  a b c financial statements for revlon  morningstar morningstarcom  retrieved    a b financials for revlon google finance  retrieved    fortune  page for revlon fortune  retrieved    model by michael gross  page   andrewtobiascom andrewtobiascom retrieved    mcgill douglas c august   cosmetics companies quietly ending animal tests the new york times   stevenson richard  pantry pride control of revlon board seen near new york times p d   macandrews  forbes holdings inc funding universe retrieved    revlon acquires sinful nail brand womens wear daily march     hills suzannah july   loccitane and yves rocher the bigname beauty brands among those ditching crueltyfree animal testing policies to sell their products to china daily mail retrieved  january    young vicki m revlon acquires colomer group for  million wwd retrieved  august    revlon to exit operations in china cut  jobs january     revlon names lorenzo delpani president ceo october     revlon inc announces election of roberto simon as executive vice president and chief financial officer  form k september     the gir